<h3> Different ways to communicate electronically </h3>

<p>There are multiple electronic communication options. It is very beneficial because it helps businesses and individuals communicate with one another without having to be in person. </p>

<p>There are many different devices you may use to communicate electronically such as a smart phone, computer, laptop or  tablet. All of them have their own features and some may not be able to do the same thing another device can. </p>
<h4>Here are a few different ways to communicate electronically:
</h4>
<ul>
  <li>Phone/text</li>
  <li>Email</li>
  <li>Social Media</li>

